Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think it is a good choice for freshman to live on campus during the first year of college.
First, most students live at home when they are at high school, they have no chance to live a union life, it would be a great experience to learn how to live with others.